title: Format_Function_Test
tags:
---
<<set $test_number = 1>>
Let's test whether format functions work. The test number is set to {$test_number}.
Ordinal numbers - I came in {$test_number}[ordinal {$test_number} one="st" two="nd" few="rd" other="th"] place.
Plurals - I've got [plural {$test_number} one="one apple" other="% apples"].
Selection - test number is [select {$select_test} 0="zero" 1="one" other="something other than zero or one"].
Format function test done!
