title: Condition_Test
tags:
---
<<set $test_number = 0>>
Let's test conditions by setting a test number to...
-> 0.
-> 1.
	<<set $test_number = 1>>
-> 2.
	<<set $test_number = 2>>
<<if $test_number == 0>>
	You will see this text if the test number is 0.
<<elseif $test_number == 1>>
	This text is displayed when the test number is 1.
<<else>>
	You've set the test number to 2, so this text is shown.
<<endif>>
Condition testing done!
